This product builds on the original concept and design of CKdpsApp by SirPHz
(https://github.com/mjb6967/CKdpsApp), a combat-log DPS meter for Throne and
Liberty. The frontend began as a fork of that project; the backend in this
repository is an independent, clean reimplementation behind the same local
WebSocket contract.

